WEBVTT

09:36.000 --> 09:38.310 line:80%
Why should I be afraid of
being laughed at?

09:38.310 --> 09:39.190 line:80%
Isn't it normal for kids to have

09:39.190 --> 09:41.120 line:80%
a few bumps and scrapes
when they're playing around?

09:41.120 --> 09:42.260 line:80%
-Stop shouting.
-Whether you have the right

09:42.260 --> 09:43.920 line:80%
to demand justice here or not,

09:44.070 --> 09:46.000 line:80%
we need to ask Fan Changning first.
